text: Nikolayevka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Nikolayevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 724 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Tuymazy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Nikolayevka, Tuymazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
